Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,thought I would sort of tell you how the day is going to go. We originally
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,allocated two hours for lunch. I think that's too long. Is that sort of boring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,after two hours? I think maybe we'll resume the lecture at 1.30. There's a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,group here from out of state. Are there a bunch of people here from Wisconsin or
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that group? Oh, goopoo. I thought the Wisconsin group, I'll meet with them in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the viewing room about 1.15. We'll meet with you especially and then we'll vacate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the viewing room for the others at 1.30 and go on the lecture. But I thought we'd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,meet together. You know, I grew up in Wisconsin and I've been back there in a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,long time. 60 years, I guess, or something. A long time. Well, the evolution of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. Do we have, we'll explain how the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,People in spiritual work are concerned with the ego. And in the 400s, people are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligent and well-read. They know that that's their problem, how to transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this ego, how to approach the ego. The reason I like the Course in Miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,workbook, it calibrates at 600. The text calibrates at 550. The difference is that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like about the textbook is that it tends to demonize the ego and set up a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And part of your mind sees the ego as the enemy. I brought my ego with me to show you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the true nature of the ego. The ego is troublesome, but it's really a pussycat when you begin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand what it's about. We have the evolution of consciousness beginning back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in time. If you've got this, on this wonderful machine here, we've got, you know, the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness – we've got paleontology, we've got Epcox.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,See life, if you understand the ego, then you begin to – you stop demonizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on. Somebody has to tell me half the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, there's no life on Mars. To speak the person on Mars, there is notсудy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew that with kinesiology before they went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They ain't done that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so, Sanyo, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, on this planet, there was no life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and then a life appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It appeared, you see, if you were going to establish life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on a, let's say, hostile, it's not really hostile,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but not friendly planet, it's just all rocks and dirt, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of this planet is molten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The center of the Earth, then, is a fireball,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which over zillions of years, quadrillions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,gradually cooled down enough that the surface
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was congenial to life circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's a fiery ball at a couple thousand degrees Fahrenheit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not too friendly to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Although life did manage, there is bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that live in the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the center of the earth, in the molten lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:04:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So life is tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would be the first principle and rule of life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if it were going to establish itself on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have to be programmed, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve its own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The core of the ego, then, is self-serving,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because without self-servingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,no existence is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Life, then, requires energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have enough energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the essence of life is to get energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The amoeba goes out there and gets energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, the first signs of life, bacteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, be careful, don't shine it in anybody's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little scared of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, this is so far long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't even know what those words mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If we calibrate what's at this time of the rock age,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,age of oldest dated rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 8, 50, with about 10 zeros after it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ago, first signs of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,actually, it's below this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacteria are at 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Algae aren't aware they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And viruses are not aware they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Virus just reproduces DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't know that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bacteria is the first, it calibrates at 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see consciousness gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpions at 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know why I never liked scorpions much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And sharks, you see, shell-crushing sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you see, life has to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-interest, self-interest is the necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it wasn't for the selfishness of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,none of us would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in demonizing selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for selfishness, you wouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because life would not have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It survives because it's interested in me, that I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough energy, enough molecules,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll eat somebody and then I'll have more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So energy acquisition, then, is necessary to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, life then evolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And birds, you see, primitive mammals, modern mammals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,over great eons of time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is completely and totally self-interested
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,until you see the animal kingdom at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We got animal kingdom there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the core of your ego better be interested in self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It better be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you won't live long enough to become spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We love the protozoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got a present from my sweet wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave me a, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A trilobite, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So we calibrated our trilobite back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crustacean at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So my trilobite at home calibrates at three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We get up to six, the fish at 20, sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how these are all self-interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe there's somebody crazy enough
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to get into a Komodo dragon's cage with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Neville Chamberlain before World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're nice to the Komodo dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bin Laden is just misguided.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we're nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're nice to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be nice with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So Komodo dragon bit the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he didn't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so he had some good karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Reptiles at 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we get to the predatory mammals, snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about predatory mammals
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is you can make them pets for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As they get older,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they revert and will kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as the lady who raised the lion found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,some years ago back in maybe the 50s,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,their ocelots were sort of a craze with ocelots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The only trouble was the ocelot got older,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he started to eat your child,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so you had to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So we find out ocelots don't work
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because their inner nature is the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, freedom is not denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom is relinquishing denial
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and seeing it as childish naivete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we see the whales and the dolphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people cheer for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,some people cheer for the dolphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for the dolphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Migratory birds, birds of prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,rodents, rhinoceros, songbirds, doves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,polar bears, grizzly bears, water buffalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a bear is fun, but he'll also kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wait long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as he gets older,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,one day he's going to get pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to get people out of spiritual naivete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,People become spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hearts and flowers and piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They walk you right over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk you right over the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's not discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Discernment is the opening of the third eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness that you just know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what is integrous and what is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the third eye of the Buddhic body opens up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to take the word of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And kinesiology certainly serves that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the water buffalo is a renowned killer of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The wolves, the hippopotamus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the hippopotamus kills more humans
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,than any other animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's always a strange statistic to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are people in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with the hippopotamus in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't really the alligator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The alligator kills a lot of people too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not their fault. It's not the hippopotamus' fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hippopotamus isn't enough to get in there with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just picked how they're going to leave this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things, some things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,become sanctified.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We did food before and after it's blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest quality food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest energy is homemade food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's then blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When you bless food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it jumps quite a few points in the calibrated energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually transform food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is made by love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates much higher than that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which is made by machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Very often makes you go weak, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a couple brands of cat food
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which I won't mention
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that my cat won't touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated them. They're below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Cat knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't eat calibrated food below 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're established brands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of all those poor kitties out there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,being forced to eat that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So we bless our kitties' food too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless this food for our kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless your kitty's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I started to say that was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it was really interesting for this new book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This new book I'm just finishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless us when it's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to tell the truth about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how popular that will make you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a famous quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot who it was. Montaigne or somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, after you tell the truth, leave town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once floating in the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huangpu River in Formosa, China
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or some other place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was full of feces,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was laying in my bunk on a minesweeper
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hear the thump, thump, thump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As we get out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His head is bumping against the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Ganges River goes by
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,100 metropolitan areas that all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,dump their sewage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The sewage of 100 metropolitan areas
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,dumps into the Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus countless dead bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,feces of all kinds of animals, humans, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ganges River,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,help me God, calibrates over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ganges River.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have permission, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,505, 510,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,515.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of spiritual intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For thousands of years, the Hindus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,worshipfully
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,bathed for purification
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Ganges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ganges is 510.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's higher than your tap water at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do the animals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the power of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by being worshipful in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one comes to a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of safety and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And through prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way you are to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,once you've owned
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and recontextualized
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you are to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a living prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get out your silly prayer card
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and go through the recitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that which a prayer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically responds to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So worshipfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in all the feces and dead bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and garbage,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the Ganges River calibrates at
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,five something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that incredible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So then the hippopotamus, you get the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to figure out how to work this thing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At 200, then, you see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a shift of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from those who live
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,rapaciously through the death of others
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by breaking the back of their neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by ripping out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,their jugular vein,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see those that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,now survive by eating grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It still needs energy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from out there, but it's in the form of grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's benign.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to kill anything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill life to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see the core of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then is rapacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now here it becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,benevolent. So you see
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the emergence of benevolence
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in the animal kingdom calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safer with a zebra
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or a gazelle or a giraffe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,than 85% of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll steal you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,blind. Deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,bison, domestic pig, elk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,dairy cow, sheep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,range cattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now when I calibrated some of these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes I did them too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A reader of one of the books
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sent me a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you calibrate something,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I'd made a difference in the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration of elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're doing calibrated energies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're in a hurry, you may do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,one time you picture
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a herd of African wild elephants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,elephants could be a male who's in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Musk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Another time I picture
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Indian elephants. Another time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember I did picture an Indian elephant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with a mahat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or what do they call them on the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahat pushing up a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you've got certain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,circus elephants. So it makes a difference
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which of those elephants you picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't always picture the same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I pictured, I remember, African
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,elephants in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And another I pictured a guy with a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,hauta on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Also we process things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We process how a thing looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,how it sounds, how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,when it gets down to microscopic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration, we don't do microscopic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What we're trying to convey is a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,generality. But there may be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,research problems in which
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a variation of a couple of degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is significant. In that point
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're going to calibrate a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,thing and what you're picturing is how your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,feels or how she
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,looks or how she sounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll have to use the same
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,way every time you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that and I'm glad he brought it to my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the elephants and there was some other
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,one in which I calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,differently. Oh, monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See the monkeys in the African wild
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tree, it gives you a different
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,energy than monkeys in a zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and gives you a different picture
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,than monkeys
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that hang out in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,places in India. The different monkeys will give you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,different calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people are just trying to get a generality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really what we usually ask is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing is either
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous or not. That's the main thing we want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,going to say that these are exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably plus or minus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book we just finished we've got at least
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just see how accurate that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,book is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The calibrations in the book I'm just finishing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,are very
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,more than 1%, 2%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,last time we did it was 3% but I corrected
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus or minus 3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it goes into print
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll recalibrate them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do want to admit that error.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the tenth step in AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're wrong you admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Something world leaders have never
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard some of the biggest names in America
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,get up there and lie through their teeth and I say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't they just admit that and say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, I mean so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And go on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just say yeah I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we see then and also a race horse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is more evolved than a regular farm horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when these animals become
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,involved with humans their consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,advances. So a kitty cat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,feline nature is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,240 but a house
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,cat jumps to about 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the same with the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dog. He becomes a family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dog. He jumps to at least 5 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the monkeys that I was
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrating one time were friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,happy monkeys at 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A gorilla is a very nice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,person to be with. Chimpanzees are
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and as we said before
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex the gray
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,trained elephant gray
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is 401.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex actually knows how to think and so does
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco. And here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,comes love yelping up through the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,chakra bypassing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole rest of the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,animal kingdom. And you got
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a kitty's purr is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,songbird's song 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And a dog's wagging tail is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,amazing? So
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness then is the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,essence of life. Life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to survive has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,self serving. So there's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,no point in feeling guilty about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ego because
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it had to be self
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,centered in order for you to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However then it evolves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,past that and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,energy begins to flow at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,200. The transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,begins at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just do that for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission in front of this audience oh lord
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to flow at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not flow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200. And the etheric
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,brain does not exist below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain starts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at 200 and it's a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of the flow of the kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,people below 200 don't have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of faulting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,them for being non-integrous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By what way would they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,means of knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So now here is your
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ego. As you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he's evolved from the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to be with your ego is to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,realize that without your ego you wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,even be here. So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The other way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to disarm is to not get polarized
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,against the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To just know that the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody jumps ahead of us in traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we hate him, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He should die, shouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he should die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.44,0:23:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,People who get in front of us in traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and drive slow are bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.03,0:24:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of denying your ego
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which led to World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you see what happened with denial?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It cost the lives of 10 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,died due to a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.86,0:24:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the best way to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.86,0:24:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,de-energize the ego is to tell the truth about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're greedy, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.15,0:24:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want more, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he wants to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to win, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.44,0:24:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.60,0:24:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He always wants to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.99,0:24:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So he hasn't learned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.99,0:24:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.99,0:24:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,than to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.40,0:24:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end what counts as succeeding
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.40,0:24:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,winning doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.40,0:25:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Every winner sooner or later
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.04,0:25:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Every winner is polarized
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.04,0:25:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually a loser
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.45,0:25:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's playing the win-lose game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.45,0:25:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We know from quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.45,0:25:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you play win-lose often enough
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.45,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,sooner or later
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the 26th decimal point
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.45,0:25:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to come up and kick you in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.92,0:25:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you listen to me now, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.04,0:25:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,than to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.04,0:25:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.72,0:25:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we dissolve the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is through love,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.72,0:25:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,through compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.72,0:25:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because we read it in a book,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.72,0:25:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,not because Krishna said it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,not because Jesus said it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.13,0:25:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but because we see it for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.13,0:25:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What else could the little bear in us do
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.64,0:26:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,except do all the candidate things
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.64,0:26:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's supposed to do for survival?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks he's supposed to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.64,0:26:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.92,0:26:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.92,0:26:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the next slide after the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.92,0:26:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll skip that one anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.50,0:26:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.04,0:26:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll skip that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.48,0:26:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll just blank it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.48,0:26:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.48,0:26:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we said it's a way to be in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.66,0:26:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.98,0:26:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to focus on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.98,0:26:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to focus on content all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.98,0:26:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.33,0:26:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.33,0:26:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can waste all the lifetimes you wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.33,0:26:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,fooling around with content.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.33,0:26:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get your content
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.45,0:26:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in context and not content,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.45,0:26:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that recontextualizes that content
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.45,0:26:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the content is no longer a problem to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to recontextualize
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.00,0:26:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.00,0:27:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing but a teddy bear within you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.00,0:27:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who's doing his duty to try and win
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.00,0:27:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because he thinks that's what he's supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.00,0:27:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought that for
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,hundreds of millions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.80,0:27:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.56,0:27:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead, win for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.27,0:27:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.28,0:27:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,People constantly send me questions
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.40,0:27:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,about various spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.40,0:27:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people are,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,oh that's really good, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.03,0:27:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always asking me to calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.03,0:27:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody or some
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.19,0:27:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,entity on the other side or something
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.19,0:27:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.64,0:27:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to be quoted as
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.64,0:27:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he said so and so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.53,0:27:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.98,0:27:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what integrity is about then
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.98,0:27:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to calibrate a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.98,0:27:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say, what is a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,pure spiritual pathway?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.43,0:28:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't glamorize itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.43,0:28:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.43,0:28:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,dramatize itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.43,0:28:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't come on with theatrical presentations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.43,0:28:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's non-exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.57,0:28:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody pays a penalty
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.40,0:28:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if they decide to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.40,0:28:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.55,0:28:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't adulate the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.55,0:28:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was the leader? That's just his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.93,0:28:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leading or teaching. Teaching is a function.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.93,0:28:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the person serves that function.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.48,0:28:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore you call them
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.60,0:28:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,respect because he's fulfilling the function.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I do the milkman who delivers the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.60,0:28:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The street cleaner cleans the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.69,0:28:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We accord them the respect
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.69,0:28:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the fact that they fulfill their function.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.69,0:28:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Without their function
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.01,0:29:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When garbage delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.01,0:29:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,removal stops on the streets of New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.01,0:29:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really a disaster. I lived there through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.01,0:29:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really learn to respect
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.01,0:29:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the garbage man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.01,0:29:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we respect people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.84,0:29:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.97,0:29:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So adulation of gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.97,0:29:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is a great trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.97,0:29:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The gurus that fall into it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a whole group of them
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.97,0:29:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other side of the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.97,0:29:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,eight or nine of them
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.97,0:29:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,all fell at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.97,0:29:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I only realized
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.66,0:29:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what the reason was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.66,0:29:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was having breakfast with somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.66,0:29:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who was a friend of Gopi Krishna
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.66,0:29:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,painted Gopi Krishna
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.66,0:29:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who wrote the famous book on Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.66,0:29:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.72,0:29:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when he first went to India
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.72,0:29:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he says
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.72,0:29:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the Indian people explained to him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.95,0:29:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not scrupulous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, scrupulosity
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.84,0:30:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a requirement
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.84,0:30:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of success in that culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.57,0:30:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying whatever you think will get the sale
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.57,0:30:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or win is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.57,0:30:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.57,0:30:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we grew up in a judo-Christian culture
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.70,0:30:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in which that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There it's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.34,0:30:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a organic culture
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.60,0:30:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and snake charmers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.60,0:30:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody who can
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.60,0:30:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,boon-boggle you and get your pennies
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.60,0:30:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.60,0:30:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.60,0:30:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point in demonizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.88,0:30:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So a true teacher then
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,teaches from
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.88,0:30:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.88,0:30:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is teaching from
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.88,0:30:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what the teacher has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.00,0:30:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't teach by
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.68,0:30:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,authority of external
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.09,0:30:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't quote something
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.09,0:31:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and then quote it to you as a teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's known as
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.46,0:31:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it stands on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.46,0:31:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrous spirituality and truth
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.46,0:31:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stands on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.52,0:31:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have quotes from famous
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.52,0:31:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.52,0:31:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What famous people think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.75,0:31:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is totally irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.75,0:31:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It stands on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.42,0:31:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.57,0:31:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has nothing to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.89,0:31:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to be gained, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.18,0:31:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What it's looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.18,0:31:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is not looking for any kind of gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.18,0:31:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't need followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.21,0:31:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they want followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.21,0:31:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine everywhere you go
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.44,0:31:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they're trailing behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.44,0:31:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to get on a streetcar
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.76,0:31:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you wonder if all your followers got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.76,0:31:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere you look you got followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.30,0:31:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Power over others and controlling others.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.52,0:31:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A good teacher doesn't tell anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.52,0:31:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how they should live.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.52,0:31:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Their personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.52,0:32:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What you should wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What you should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a spiritual teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.52,0:32:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,be interested in your personal life?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.52,0:32:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That could be more and more boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.52,0:32:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to get divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.62,0:32:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.62,0:32:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to stay with her? Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.62,0:32:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to eat meat? Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.62,0:32:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to eat meat on Fridays? Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.07,0:32:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat meat on Fridays? Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.20,0:32:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's worse than any other day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.20,0:32:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat meat on a good Friday, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.44,0:32:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are really...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.78,0:32:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you gotta wear a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you gotta wear a hat or not wear a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.78,0:32:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your hat off. Respect God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.78,0:32:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Respect God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.22,0:32:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, put my hat on or off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.44,0:32:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.01,0:32:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.01,0:32:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need fancy strange garb.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.68,0:32:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.68,0:33:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.39,0:33:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.42,0:33:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Piety is a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.42,0:33:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a naturalness
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.32,0:33:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to the way you are within the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.32,0:33:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,True piety is worshipful
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.32,0:33:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.54,0:33:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you present
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.88,0:33:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.52,0:33:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.68,0:33:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.68,0:33:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In so doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.95,0:33:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,one serves God and one's fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.42,0:33:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no desire to control people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.42,0:33:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have them sign up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.42,0:33:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.42,0:33:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You sign up three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.61,0:33:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get an extra $50.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.61,0:33:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So there isn't any market level marketing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.68,0:33:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,multi-level marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.25,0:33:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing stands on its own
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.25,0:33:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,due to its own integrity, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.17,0:33:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not interested in money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.17,0:33:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interested in covering expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.17,0:34:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Expenses are quite high, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.52,0:34:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Radisson cost you about 10 grand up in front
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.52,0:34:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,just to walk in the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.16,0:34:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And there were other places we wanted to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.16,0:34:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was even more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.16,0:34:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you cover the expense
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.16,0:34:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you've got to have enough left over
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.16,0:34:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for operations
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.16,0:34:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because you have to have quite a sizable staff
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.16,0:34:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as time goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.16,0:34:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got half a dozen people
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.16,0:34:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,answering the phone and shipping out things
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.16,0:34:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and mailing and answering questions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.36,0:34:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and making reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.36,0:34:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead from 12 to 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.36,0:34:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'll stop at 12.30.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.36,0:34:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At 1.15 I'll meet with that group in the side room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.42,0:34:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remembered somebody said
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.42,0:34:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there's leaflets telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.42,0:34:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there's restaurants that'll give you a discount
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.55,0:34:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.55,0:34:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And those leaflets are out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.83,0:34:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.83,0:34:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to calibrate a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.05,0:34:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.05,0:34:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because whether a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.05,0:34:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is right for a prisoner or not depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.05,0:34:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When you begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.05,0:35:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you a great place to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.08,0:35:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's to join the scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.08,0:35:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy Scouts and Girl Scouts of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They calibrate way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.18,0:35:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They calibrate way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.18,0:35:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And Eagle Scout calibrates even higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.18,0:35:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what they calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.18,0:35:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.34,0:35:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A good place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.34,0:35:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Scouts start you off right at 4.50 or 4.60
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.34,0:35:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.34,0:35:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hell of a good place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.34,0:35:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That beats about 90% of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.34,0:35:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to start out at 4.60.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.34,0:35:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to go
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.81,0:35:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to strange places and seek out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.81,0:35:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,people in esoteric garb.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.81,0:35:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because those are dramatizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.91,0:35:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And India is the home of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.91,0:35:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They've learned the art of spiritual seduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.91,0:35:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The art of spiritual seduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.91,0:35:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.05,0:35:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in a teacher is somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.05,0:35:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who has the recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.31,0:35:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of the relatively erudite spiritual seekers
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.31,0:35:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,alias that you won't waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.31,0:35:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested in status.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.01,0:36:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested in money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.01,0:36:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't self-assert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.08,0:36:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't design any special titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.08,0:36:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the title of the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.52,0:36:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're teaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.52,0:36:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then I guess teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.52,0:36:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a swimmer, you'd be swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a skier, you'd be the skier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.52,0:36:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The group skier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.52,0:36:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So teacher just does teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.52,0:36:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's the function.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.52,0:36:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So one is one's function
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.52,0:36:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and one's function comes out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.52,0:36:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.52,0:36:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the true teacher then
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.60,0:36:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is merely
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.99,0:36:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the reflection of the inner knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.99,0:36:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no personal self
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.08,0:36:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that decides to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.08,0:36:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't process things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.08,0:36:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.08,0:36:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.08,0:36:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then speaks spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.08,0:36:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.14,0:36:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there is no design.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:37:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything happens spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.32,0:37:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When you become
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.36,0:37:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you can be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.36,0:37:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to the utmost, to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.36,0:37:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you are a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.36,0:37:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Recitations are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.78,0:37:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We were talking about piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.72,0:37:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain level of which
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.72,0:37:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,piety is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.79,0:37:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,natural for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.79,0:37:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute I look at this audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.79,0:37:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel worshipful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.79,0:37:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.88,0:37:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if I don't watch it, tears begin to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.88,0:37:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of joyful ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.87,0:37:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.78,0:37:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,another kind of piety
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.78,0:37:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that's sort of holier than now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.78,0:37:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,piety.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.78,0:37:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Draped in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.78,0:37:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,robes and incense
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.78,0:37:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and dingle bells and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.87,0:37:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of a dramatization.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.87,0:37:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It can itself become an addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.87,0:38:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like asceticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.22,0:38:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through asceticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.22,0:38:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can live without anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.22,0:38:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.22,0:38:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.48,0:38:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,extreme poverty and asceticism
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.48,0:38:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes in itself an addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.48,0:38:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you transcend that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.51,0:38:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright to have stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to have an aversion
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.50,0:38:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't have to have an attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.59,0:38:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the person is looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.59,0:38:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when they want to calibrate a true teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.59,0:38:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is somebody who is naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.59,0:38:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the expression of that which they have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.59,0:38:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they don't require
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.59,0:38:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,falsity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.59,0:38:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because all they are is just being
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.59,0:38:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that which they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.68,0:38:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To just be that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.29,0:38:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To just be that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Satchmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.36,0:38:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just is who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.36,0:38:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Louis Armstrong calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.36,0:38:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,way up there, 5 or 10 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.36,0:38:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of the top guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.36,0:38:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Satchmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.36,0:38:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just came from universal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.36,0:39:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just was what he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.36,0:39:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't have to make any poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.42,0:39:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't have to control people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.42,0:39:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't need anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.64,0:39:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.64,0:39:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what you should wear,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.64,0:39:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who you should be with,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.64,0:39:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all about your sex life,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.86,0:39:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what you should eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.86,0:39:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,meat, fish, what.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.86,0:39:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-controlling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.31,0:39:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So freedom then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.76,0:39:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom is the natural expression
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.76,0:39:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.88,0:39:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you find a teacher that you're comfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.88,0:39:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you grow along
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.88,0:39:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you may go through
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.92,0:39:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a progression of teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.84,0:39:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the teacher who is right
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.84,0:39:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,solves this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.84,0:39:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're ready to move on to another teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.84,0:39:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because you've moved along.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.84,0:39:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've learned what this teacher has to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.04,0:39:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual teaching of course
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.04,0:40:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.04,0:40:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from an advanced consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.04,0:40:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the content at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.04,0:40:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the frequency and the vibration
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.04,0:40:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.04,0:40:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the frequency and the vibration
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.04,0:40:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of the aura, of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.04,0:40:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.55,0:40:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See, content is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.55,0:40:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is prayers and mantras and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.55,0:40:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes them work
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.55,0:40:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it generates a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.64,0:40:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's actually teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.64,0:40:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.74,0:40:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.00,0:40:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The frequency of the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.00,0:40:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the vibration of the aura
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.00,0:40:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.35,0:40:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,by your ascent becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.35,0:40:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,trained in your own aura
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.35,0:40:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.35,0:40:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the Buddha meant
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.35,0:40:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.99,0:40:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.99,0:40:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in my understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.99,0:40:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,my inner understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.99,0:40:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is the frequency and the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.99,0:40:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of that has within it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.99,0:40:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.31,0:41:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The information that you need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.31,0:41:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,at a certain point is encoded in the frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.31,0:41:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Having brought that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.14,0:41:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,frequency into your own aura
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.43,0:41:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.43,0:41:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a state eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.43,0:41:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.62,0:41:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How many here are going to be enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.78,0:41:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody! God bless you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.78,0:41:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would you be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.74,0:41:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I prepare
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.74,0:41:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,people for along the whole trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.74,0:41:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in either this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.12,0:41:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or some lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.19,0:41:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you reach the final door
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.19,0:41:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and at that point
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.32,0:41:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.67,0:41:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,anything because you don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.67,0:41:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,any memory to remember it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.67,0:41:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, oh I'll remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.89,0:41:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when I get there. No you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.89,0:41:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There ain't nothing to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.89,0:41:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They took away your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.15,0:41:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot God's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.78,0:41:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,number. What the hell was his number?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.78,0:42:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because it's very
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.39,0:42:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,vivid, the knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.64,0:42:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowingness replaces
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.64,0:42:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,thinkingness. You don't need thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.64,0:42:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,what you need is knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.22,0:42:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you walk through the last
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.22,0:42:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,door, there's a moment of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.22,0:42:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,terror because
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.44,0:42:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing left to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.44,0:42:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to God except
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.44,0:42:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.54,0:42:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you think you have been
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.54,0:42:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,through all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.54,0:42:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The core of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.54,0:42:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You now surrender to God
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.53,0:42:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and now
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.53,0:42:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you die for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.53,0:42:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and only and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.82,0:42:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The other time you just left the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.82,0:42:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't go for melodrama
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.82,0:42:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,about dying. Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.43,0:42:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have we all died here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.43,0:42:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Quizzle. You're out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.43,0:42:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.43,0:42:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All the drama on this side. God bless it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.87,0:43:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this time
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.87,0:43:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you're really going to need
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.87,0:43:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness because without the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.87,0:43:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it's terrifying to walk
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.83,0:43:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,through because you realize you are
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.83,0:43:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,actually walking into actual
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.83,0:43:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,death. This is death
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.83,0:43:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that you do have to give up your
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.83,0:43:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,life. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.11,0:43:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the full understanding of that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.11,0:43:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,comes forth. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.56,0:43:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,out of non-thinkingness because
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.56,0:43:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're beyond thought at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.56,0:43:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no thinking to think with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.56,0:43:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no thinker left.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.94,0:43:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Comes the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.26,0:43:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher must have
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.26,0:43:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute concrete certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.26,0:43:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The only concrete
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.77,0:43:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute certainty for which
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.77,0:43:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,one is taking karmic responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.77,0:43:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for that which is being said
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.77,0:43:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything I say I take
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.77,0:43:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic responsibility and I'm very
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.77,0:43:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,aware of the price of error.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.77,0:43:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At the doorway the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.32,0:43:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,comes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.08,0:44:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To surrender life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.08,0:44:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.15,0:44:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Comes out of like Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.15,0:44:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To walk straight ahead no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.56,0:44:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all fear is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.56,0:44:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.52,0:44:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe except this instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.18,0:44:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay for 99.99%.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.18,0:44:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the last iota?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.18,0:44:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And there takes the great
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.04,0:44:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,courage. There you walk
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.20,0:44:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,through it and you experience
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.20,0:44:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,death. I won't kid you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.20,0:44:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Agonizing. You experience
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.20,0:44:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.41,0:44:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what carries you through
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.41,0:44:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is the energy field of the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.41,0:44:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,aura. See the frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.41,0:44:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,cast within it the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.51,0:44:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing said that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.51,0:44:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other beings there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.51,0:44:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget other beings. There are no other
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.51,0:44:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,higher beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.51,0:44:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No spiritual guides or whatever crap
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.51,0:44:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they think about. No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.51,0:44:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met any along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.51,0:45:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And they aren't there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.51,0:45:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the inner knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.51,0:45:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to walk straight ahead no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.51,0:45:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.51,0:45:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I repeat
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.51,0:45:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where I heard it originally apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.51,0:45:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,from the aura of the Buddha or
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.51,0:45:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the great
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.40,0:45:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers of the ancient Vedas. I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.40,0:45:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where in history. I never tracked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.40,0:45:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.68,0:45:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's encoded as a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.88,0:45:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,frequency. And when
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.94,0:45:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you need it you've reached that frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.94,0:45:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and at that frequency the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.94,0:45:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is known.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.74,0:45:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you walk through.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.09,0:45:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all splendor
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.09,0:45:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.97,0:45:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the purpose then
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.40,0:45:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.47,0:45:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to share with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.47,0:46:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the students
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.47,0:46:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,where the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.63,0:46:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,has been and where
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.63,0:46:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he knows he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.66,0:46:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And doesn't pretend to be beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.66,0:46:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The integrity of many organizations
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.01,0:46:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,like AA etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.01,0:46:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You see all of them humility.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.01,0:46:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Humility is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.17,0:46:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the courage to tell the truth about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.17,0:46:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the true teacher will say
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.17,0:46:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you know I got this far
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.17,0:46:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you want to go farther
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.17,0:46:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to find somebody who teaches that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.17,0:46:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Teachers of religion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.49,0:46:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,do not teach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.49,0:46:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll say look
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.49,0:46:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong to a religion and we teach
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.49,0:46:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,such and such and that's as far as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.49,0:46:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So that person is being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.49,0:46:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He says I only believe in God transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.49,0:46:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of the mystic
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.88,0:46:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is still
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.88,0:46:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.60,0:46:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We gave up burning them at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.60,0:46:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Or putting them under house arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.60,0:46:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.60,0:46:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Galileo was put under house arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.85,0:47:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.85,0:47:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you move from religion
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.20,0:47:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which has its core spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.20,0:47:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say I want to transcend religion
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.20,0:47:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.20,0:47:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to where religion came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to rediscover
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.20,0:47:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual core out of which
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.20,0:47:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a religion arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you have to go from
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.80,0:47:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional religion into spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.80,0:47:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.80,0:47:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,brings you in contact with the world's great religions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.80,0:47:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The great
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.89,0:47:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vedas out of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.89,0:47:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The enlightened masters
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.89,0:47:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,arose in the Vedic
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.89,0:47:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and Aryan culture
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.89,0:47:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of ancient India.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.89,0:47:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They were enlightened gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.89,0:47:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by 7,000 BC.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.96,0:47:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,7,000 BC.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.48,0:47:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a great
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.48,0:47:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened master.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.74,0:47:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,5,000 BC.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.74,0:47:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha came along
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.00,0:47:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,500 BC
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.25,0:48:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reason the Buddha was never a Christian
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.25,0:48:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is Christ hadn't been born for another 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.25,0:48:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here people
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.00,0:48:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,knock the Buddha. He's not a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.00,0:48:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a heathen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.41,0:48:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ wasn't born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.44,0:48:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the core of all truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.04,0:48:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher has to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.45,0:48:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,have humility
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.45,0:48:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of knowing where the limitations are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.45,0:48:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingness to admit a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.87,0:48:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I miscalibrated monkeys
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.93,0:48:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I miscalibrated monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.93,0:48:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have been monkeying around
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.05,0:48:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.05,0:48:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkeying with the figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.05,0:48:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.53,0:48:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to make that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.53,0:48:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That by their fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.92,0:48:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you should know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.40,0:48:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be impressed by the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.40,0:49:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.43,0:49:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the kundalini energy comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.43,0:49:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it performs the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.43,0:49:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.65,0:49:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you that performs the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.65,0:49:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.65,0:49:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,miracle workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.75,0:49:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the kundalini is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.75,0:49:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It will heal that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.75,0:49:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to which it is destined to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.75,0:49:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't select it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.94,0:49:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think oh look at that poor sick woman there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.94,0:49:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all crippled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.94,0:49:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And start sending her healing energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.94,0:49:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.13,0:49:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The kundalini energy does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.55,0:49:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't consult you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.55,0:49:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It just goes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.61,0:49:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden the lady who's all
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.61,0:49:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,twisted up looks at you and goes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.61,0:49:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,walks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.00,0:49:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.00,0:49:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.16,0:49:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the kundalini energy is not
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.16,0:49:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.57,0:49:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't perform miracles on the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.57,0:49:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.73,0:50:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it acts of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.73,0:50:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a divine energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.73,0:50:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it comes from on high.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.73,0:50:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a conduit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.73,0:50:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a telephone, telegraph
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.73,0:50:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,radio station.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.73,0:50:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And it goes there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.73,0:50:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a radio station.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.44,0:50:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the source of that divine energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.44,0:50:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've all become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.78,0:50:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.78,0:50:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your past is healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.03,0:50:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.83,0:50:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And from this point on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.98,0:50:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we have become
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.98,0:50:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we are each one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.98,0:50:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a prayer to this world
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.98,0:50:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.63,0:50:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At 1.15 I'll meet with the Wisconsin group.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.63,0:50:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll slice cheese and sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.04,0:51:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At 1.30
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.04,0:51:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the main group will resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.04,0:51:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheboygan is the world's foremost
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.04,0:51:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,producer of sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.74,0:51:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'll tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.74,0:51:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,good old Wisconsin summer sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.74,0:51:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we met with
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.35,0:51:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a group there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.38,0:51:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're a little bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.89,0:51:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know how long it would take
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.89,0:51:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to get in town, out of town
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.89,0:51:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and meet with the group and get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.37,0:51:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to just bring
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.37,0:51:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the group did bring up
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.53,0:51:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.20,0:51:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual errors is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.20,0:51:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there's two of them. One is falling into the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.20,0:51:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The upper astral, the middle astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.27,0:51:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which the New Agers tend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.27,0:51:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle astral more.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.27,0:51:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then altered states of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.27,0:51:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See, altered states of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.27,0:51:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,like learning biofeedback
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.27,0:51:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to go into alpha states, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.27,0:52:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And various altered breathing styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.27,0:52:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that's artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.27,0:52:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can create an altered state
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.27,0:52:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,which is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.27,0:52:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do astral projection
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.27,0:52:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and all kinds of wondrous tricks with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.43,0:52:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.38,0:52:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you don't have to do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.38,0:52:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a thing happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.38,0:52:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.38,0:52:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a you doing a certain practice
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.38,0:52:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a thing happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.38,0:52:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand? That's dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.96,0:52:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.96,0:52:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So to save 60 lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.47,0:52:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee 60 lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.47,0:52:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,if you get
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.94,0:52:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the way to be in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.94,0:52:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.71,0:52:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is like allowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.32,0:52:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.32,0:52:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the big bypass.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.32,0:53:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I want you to forget cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.32,0:53:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.42,0:53:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cause
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.42,0:53:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.42,0:53:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.41,0:53:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,being what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.41,0:53:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.64,0:53:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite field of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.64,0:53:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.64,0:53:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.64,0:53:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.15,0:53:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,coalesces out of the totality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.15,0:53:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.21,0:53:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and its potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.21,0:53:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is expressed then
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.21,0:53:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,within form.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.21,0:53:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing is causing the cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.21,0:53:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.21,0:53:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got that last slide?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.21,0:53:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.02,0:53:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes the actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.02,0:53:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality is the product
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.02,0:53:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.02,0:53:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality is in the non-linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.02,0:53:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really within
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.80,0:54:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the morphogenetic fields
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.80,0:54:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of, what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.63,0:54:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.98,0:54:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in form. So evolution occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.98,0:54:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.98,0:54:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the invisible realm
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.08,0:54:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then by intentionality
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.08,0:54:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it manifests forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.08,0:54:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see there's no transitory
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.08,0:54:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,forms. You don't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.08,0:54:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,see a zebra
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.08,0:54:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.08,0:54:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes out zebra, it comes out
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.08,0:54:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,horse, it's complete and total when it comes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.08,0:54:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So the evolution is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.08,0:54:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,occurring in the invisible domain
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.08,0:54:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it appears
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.08,0:54:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so that evolution and creation are one
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.08,0:54:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.08,0:54:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution is the way creation appears
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.08,0:54:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,sequentially to perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.08,0:54:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuous and ongoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.36,0:54:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has no beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.65,0:54:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.10,0:54:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the previous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.10,0:54:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Content, field and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.09,0:54:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,content and field.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.09,0:55:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.97,0:55:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.97,0:55:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to get God on the slide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.73,0:55:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is content. This is Newtonian
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.73,0:55:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,science, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.12,0:55:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now whether a thing manifests or not
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.12,0:55:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on several
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.12,0:55:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,things. One is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.12,0:55:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the favorability of conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.12,0:55:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore you can put
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.31,0:55:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a seed in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.47,0:55:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.69,0:55:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is it has a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.79,0:55:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality to become an
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.79,0:55:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,actuality. But nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.85,0:55:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,can force it to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.85,0:55:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Under favorable conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.01,0:55:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,then. So it's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.01,0:55:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic design is that under favorable
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.01,0:55:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.01,0:55:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.01,0:55:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But you cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.43,0:55:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,force a flower to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.43,0:55:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't force it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.78,0:56:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a turtle either.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.78,0:56:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't believe in karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.20,0:56:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, well how come a butterfly isn't a turtle then?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.20,0:56:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.20,0:56:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.20,0:56:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the flower has the karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.20,0:56:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a flower and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.20,0:56:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth cannot be
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.35,0:56:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,defined except within context.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.35,0:56:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Except within context
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.35,0:56:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing is true except under certain
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.35,0:56:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions. So the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.35,0:56:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,conditions are the proximate field.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.35,0:56:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.54,0:56:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,this is political climate,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.54,0:56:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.54,0:56:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause is not the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.59,0:56:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation of phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.59,0:56:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.59,0:56:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.81,0:56:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is an arbitrary selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.81,0:56:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is in continuous flow
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.81,0:56:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you say
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.81,0:56:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,this moment started now, this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.81,0:56:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,started there, well you just picked it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.81,0:56:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as a moment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.81,0:56:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment is all in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.81,0:57:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no moments in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.42,0:57:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore there is no happenings to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.42,0:57:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.52,0:57:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gets you off the hook with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.52,0:57:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So one
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.30,0:57:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,inherits by karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.30,0:57:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution over
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.43,0:57:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,great periods of time
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.26,0:57:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.26,0:57:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which by intention
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.26,0:57:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or by the power of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.26,0:57:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.26,0:57:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I always liken
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.82,0:57:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God as an infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.82,0:57:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.27,0:57:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know how an electromagnetic
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.27,0:57:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,condenser works.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.27,0:57:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An electromagnetic condenser is still
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.27,0:57:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,until you present it with a charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.27,0:57:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.27,0:57:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the charges line up on the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.27,0:57:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,electromagnetic condenser
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.07,0:57:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,equal and opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.07,0:57:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to the charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.07,0:57:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you present it with a lot of electrons
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.07,0:58:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it will automatically, so it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.07,0:58:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,only reacts to that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.07,0:58:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,presented to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.07,0:58:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of consciousness then
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.09,0:58:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is still unmoving,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.09,0:58:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.09,0:58:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.70,0:58:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the giant electromagnetic field
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.70,0:58:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in which all the us
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.70,0:58:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,little iron filings line up
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.70,0:58:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of our design.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.96,0:58:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.04,0:58:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the freedom to choose
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.04,0:58:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,within the options
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.04,0:58:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have karmically earned
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.04,0:58:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to have presented to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.36,0:58:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot say yes or no
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.36,0:58:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to becoming a turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.36,0:58:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.20,0:58:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.20,0:58:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,gravitates by
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.64,0:58:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.25,0:58:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.25,0:58:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically aligns itself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.25,0:58:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the field over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.41,0:58:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.41,0:59:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, there is nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.41,0:59:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,paddling your canoe except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.41,0:59:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has the rudder on your
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.41,0:59:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,destiny except yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.60,0:59:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.60,0:59:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That which by choice
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.45,0:59:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you choose determines
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.45,0:59:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,where you settle out
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.45,0:59:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,within the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.45,0:59:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So like is attracted to like
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.45,0:59:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.45,0:59:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,each one filters.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.55,0:59:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So as we leave the body one automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.55,0:59:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is aligned
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.55,0:59:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,with the field of that which
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.55,0:59:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.19,0:59:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no necessity for an arbitrary god
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.19,0:59:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to give you a good smack
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.21,0:59:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for being bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.53,0:59:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are in hell already.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.53,0:59:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Having chosen hell
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.79,0:59:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,some guy will blow up a big building
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.79,0:59:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.79,0:59:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, well I know I am destined for hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.01,0:59:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.56,0:59:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Having been there I don't advise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.56,1:00:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Blowing up people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.77,1:00:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's just the upper level of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.77,1:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.04,1:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,anything out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.04,1:00:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.27,1:00:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.27,1:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as a perpetrator or a victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.29,1:00:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one brings to himself
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.29,1:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,his own
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.32,1:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,consequences of his own karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.32,1:00:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.68,1:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at birth
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.80,1:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,already has a calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.80,1:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Each person at birth
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.80,1:00:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is born in the optimal
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.80,1:00:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.09,1:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstances
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.09,1:00:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of your birth are perfect
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.09,1:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.25,1:00:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,designed for learning.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.37,1:00:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.37,1:00:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with this group.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.50,1:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstances of one's birth
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.50,1:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.72,1:00:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstances of your birth
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.72,1:01:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.72,1:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For that which you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.08,1:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.90,1:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold Wisconsin winters
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.90,1:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.42,1:01:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,18 miles a day on a bicycle
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.42,1:01:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a Wisconsin winter
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.42,1:01:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with 100 pounds of newspapers
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.68,1:01:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,was what I needed
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.68,1:01:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.03,1:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what would you call it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.03,1:01:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Steely determination no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.22,1:01:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite anything
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.22,1:01:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you grit your teeth and you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.22,1:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How to walk ahead straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.60,1:01:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That got me through medical school.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.60,1:01:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You try working your way through medical school
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.60,1:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.60,1:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,100 hours a week as an intern for $100 a month.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.60,1:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,People talk about low paying nowadays
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.60,1:01:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.28,1:01:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,$100 a month for 100 hours a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.28,1:01:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the steely
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.30,1:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,determination that it takes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.30,1:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess that was
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.30,1:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect to learn that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.30,1:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,steeliness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.30,1:02:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That walk ahead no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.30,1:02:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when the great test
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.30,1:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of it came
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.75,1:02:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the walk straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.39,1:02:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.39,1:02:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,came up in spades.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.39,1:02:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I didn't realize that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.39,1:02:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.92,1:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point bewailing one's birth
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.92,1:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point feeling sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.92,1:02:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for people.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.92,1:02:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sentimentality calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.92,1:02:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gets a lot of air time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.79,1:02:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's always
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.79,1:02:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.62,1:02:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always somebody's fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.62,1:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So the newest paradigm of reality
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.62,1:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is nothing is anybody's fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.62,1:02:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the fault of somebody out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.62,1:02:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Society, society.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.62,1:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.13,1:02:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the perpetrator victim
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.13,1:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the core of Marxism
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.36,1:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrates 130.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.36,1:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The perpetrator victim model
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.36,1:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,has had a very derogatory
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.36,1:03:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,detrimental
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.06,1:03:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,effect on the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.06,1:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,quality of the fabric of society
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.06,1:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in which one is always looking for
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.06,1:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilty
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.06,1:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilty one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.83,1:03:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.47,1:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh truth keeps
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.45,1:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,disappearing all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.45,1:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did we pay rent on?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's saving electricity
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.28,1:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.86,1:03:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the infinite
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.86,1:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.76,1:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,all encompassing fuel
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.76,1:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.76,1:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,omnipotent, omnipresent,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.76,1:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,omniscient.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.64,1:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As one lets go of the limitations
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.64,1:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of form
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.96,1:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and one progresses beyond this
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.96,1:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,one comes into the field
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.96,1:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.38,1:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what speaking
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.38,1:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what is speaking to you today
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.38,1:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.26,1:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.26,1:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It speaks spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.38,1:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.38,1:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.88,1:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes to you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.88,1:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with sudden surprise.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.68,1:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the belief there's a you
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.68,1:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,causing all these things to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.68,1:04:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the trick of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.81,1:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is to claim credit for a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.81,1:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught it once doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.81,1:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego claims credit
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.32,1:04:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for what is actually spontaneous
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.32,1:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it takes about
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.32,1:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,1 ten-thousandth of a second
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.32,1:04:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1 ten-thousandth of a second
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.74,1:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that's when the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.38,1:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,said you could glimpse
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.72,1:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate infinite truth
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.72,1:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is between two thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.72,1:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,no it's not between two thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.72,1:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's right prior to two thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.11,1:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,between two thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.11,1:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of sets up the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.20,1:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Newtonian image
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.20,1:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of thoughts being like
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.20,1:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,billiard balls
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.20,1:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,where one thought is causing another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.20,1:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Every thought is arising
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.68,1:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.68,1:05:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every thought is arising
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.32,1:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,out of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.32,1:05:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to that thought
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.16,1:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.16,1:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find right now
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.16,1:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,at the back of your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.54,1:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a still field
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.54,1:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which doesn't do anything
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.92,1:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or say anything
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.92,1:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but registers everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.92,1:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unverbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.92,1:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity for hearingness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.11,1:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity for knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.11,1:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is actually silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.62,1:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the silence
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.63,1:05:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,arises
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.63,1:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,out of sort of an
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.63,1:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of a thought
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.63,1:06:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,dogginess
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.75,1:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and then if you allow that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.75,1:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,thought to progress
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.75,1:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it's going to become old rover
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.75,1:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's going to be old rover
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.75,1:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was hit by the truck
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.75,1:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and then how we all cried
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.97,1:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,redoing rover
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.00,1:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,getting run over by the truck
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.00,1:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,rerunning the whole story
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.12,1:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.12,1:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.99,1:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even rover yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.99,1:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,By focused meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.99,1:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see how this
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.99,1:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,once you let it loose
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.99,1:06:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it begins to amplify itself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.11,1:06:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're enamored of our thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.11,1:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As you watch the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.11,1:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.65,1:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,they crest and then they fall away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.65,1:06:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.65,1:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,be quiet
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.65,1:06:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because contemplation
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.65,1:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is a way of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.65,1:06:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a contemplative way of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.91,1:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore it's continuous
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.97,1:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.97,1:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to be something
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.97,1:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you separate yourself from the world
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.07,1:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,go off, go into a very special state
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.07,1:07:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of postures
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.07,1:07:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and breathing and weird things
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.48,1:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that's separate from all dayness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.48,1:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so you go into a great state
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.48,1:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.48,1:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then you get up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.48,1:07:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.48,1:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.57,1:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation is good for
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.57,1:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,discerning how all this happens
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.57,1:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.96,1:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in a focused meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.06,1:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as you watch
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.06,1:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the thoughts arise
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.06,1:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.06,1:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,they are like the cresting of a wave
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.06,1:07:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and no sooner do they crest
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.06,1:07:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,then they're falling away
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.06,1:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so thoughts are like music
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.06,1:07:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,no sooner do you hear the tone of the music
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.06,1:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that tone is already fading away
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.88,1:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,anxiety
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.88,1:08:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or always trying to control the future
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.88,1:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,anticipate the future
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.88,1:08:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so they live in front of the wave
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.17,1:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they're always one up
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.17,1:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and always anxious about the next moment
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.17,1:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to control the next moment
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.56,1:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,people who live on the back of the wave
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.56,1:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,are clinging to the moment
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.56,1:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just left
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.48,1:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't let that last tone of music go
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.48,1:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they're trying to make it last longer
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.48,1:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're constantly ruminating
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.48,1:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,about the past
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.48,1:08:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so these people are frightened of the future
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.87,1:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,clinging to the past
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.96,1:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so you focus your attention
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.96,1:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,your awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.96,1:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on the exact presence
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.96,1:08:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is the crest
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.25,1:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,now the crest itself
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.25,1:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is arising out of an intention
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.25,1:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,intentionality of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.48,1:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this intentionality
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.48,1:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is an enamour, a hypnotic state
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.48,1:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.64,1:08:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the wanting to think
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.64,1:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll find that thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.64,1:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming from an intention
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.70,1:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can finally actually find
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.70,1:09:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the source within the silent field itself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.70,1:09:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go of the intentionality
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.70,1:09:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of thinkingness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.70,1:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what good is that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.46,1:09:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you discover
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.46,1:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that it has no life of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.46,1:09:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming out of something else
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.29,1:09:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a life lived as a prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.29,1:09:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,one's life lived as a contemplative style
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.29,1:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is to me
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.84,1:09:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the most rapid
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.84,1:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and rewarding
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.84,1:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,means of spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.84,1:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware at all times
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.11,1:09:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.11,1:09:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to be what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.81,1:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,like a mudra
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.81,1:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what a mudra is
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.81,1:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a hand position
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.23,1:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to be so that your life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.23,1:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is a presentation to God
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.23,1:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as you are
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.26,1:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am as I am
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.26,1:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to thee oh Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.51,1:09:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and to thee do I surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.51,1:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I have become
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.87,1:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,other than that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.87,1:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what would you have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.87,1:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing further
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.87,1:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to do
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.90,1:10:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,one lives one's life
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.54,1:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,like a mudra
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.54,1:10:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so to pray
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.34,1:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.44,1:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,one holds one's consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.44,1:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thusly
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.44,1:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit knows
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.14,1:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what you mean by that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.14,1:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost my dog
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.65,1:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.88,1:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to find my doggie
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.88,1:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,every time Kitty gets lost
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.68,1:10:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just go like that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.03,1:10:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kitty gets found
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.03,1:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I make a big donation
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.33,1:10:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to the church
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.33,1:11:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.40,1:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,does it for you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.40,1:11:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.84,1:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.39,1:11:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is effortless
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.39,1:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cork floating
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.57,1:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the ocean
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.57,1:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to be
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.59,1:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.59,1:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in supplication to divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.59,1:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.20,1:11:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,summons forth
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.70,1:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite powers of the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.70,1:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in your behalf
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.50,1:11:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to do anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.70,1:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.70,1:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a cork
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.70,1:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and you automatically rise
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.86,1:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,not because there is a me
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.86,1:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,doing that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.40,1:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but by virtue of that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.40,1:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which you have become
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.44,1:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,one floats higher and higher
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.44,1:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in the water
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.56,1:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.58,1:12:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to me spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.58,1:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is effortless
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.58,1:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a decision
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.54,1:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an intention
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.34,1:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that intention then aligns you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.34,1:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with whatever you need to be aligned with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.34,1:12:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a decent regret
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.54,1:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,takes care of the past
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.28,1:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,trust, faith and surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.28,1:12:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,takes care of the future
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.63,1:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the present moment
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.63,1:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have any problems
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.20,1:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,consequently
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.20,1:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what would the mind think about
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.71,1:12:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what would you think about mind
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.86,1:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you would probably fight for existence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.86,1:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going to fight for existence
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.86,1:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has no reality
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.68,1:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to be killed
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.68,1:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to kill your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.68,1:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't even exist
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.35,1:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it beat before it starts
